      <p><a href="#smug" aria-describedby="footnote-label" id="smug-ref">As someone who knows a little code,</a> it’s easy to be like, “Hey, just learn to code”. However, stepping out of your knowledge base and comfort zone can be a scary place. It can even be daunting just knowing where to begin.
    </section>

